%h2
  Adding items from your Asset Library
  
%p
  Sometimes you might need to add a picture or a link to another item from your Asset Library.
  
%p
  %strong
    NOTE:
  You will need the
  %em
    asset number
  of the asset you want to use. This asset number can be found in the web address within the Asset Library.
  
%table{:summary => "Textile Commands"}
  %tr
    %th{:width => "33%"}
      Formatting
    %th{:width => "33%"}
      Textile modifiers
    %th{:width => "33%"}
      Result
      
  %tr
    %th
      Add an item from your Asset Library
    %td
      !asset:4!
    %td
      = image_tag "help/help-kitty.jpg"
      
  %tr
    %th
      Add a thumbnail from your Asset Library
    %td
      !asset:4/thumb!:asset:4
    %td
      = image_tag "help/help-kitty-small.jpg"
  %tr
    %th
      Link to an item in your Asset Library
    %td
      "filename":asset:4
    %td
      %a{:href => "/images/help/help-kitty.jpg"}
        filename
  %tr
    %th
      Link to a thumbnail in your Asset Library
    %td
      "filename":asset:4/preview
    %td
      %a{:href => "/images/help/help-kitty-small.jpg"}
        filename
        
        
        
